name: Vessels 185: Cosper
description:
The Palace has the best of the best in charge of security.  Not many know it but Cosper is actually Dutch’s partner behind the scenes.  She is considered to be one of the most beautiful women on the colony and has a flair for dramatic aesthetic choices.  She often changes her hair and skin colour depending on her mood.  

Cosper has made significant modifications to her natural abilities including the ‘MOTHER’ system of nano-spy drones which feed back to her live on the happenings in The Palace.  Nothing gets past this lady.  Her and Dutch are real power players in colony society.
